m version 26.1, Scoro removes notifications older than two years across sites. This is presented as a performance improvement. The cleanup affects notifications only, not the records the notifications reference.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/">https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/</a></p>
