 the Help button in the top-right of the interface.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/">https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/</a></p>
";s:11:"format-info";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}s:7:"summary";s:74:"Scoro relocates ELI chat to Help Station | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:12:"snippet-text";s:74:"Scoro relocates ELI chat to Help Station | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:6:"draft?";b:0;s:10:"scheduled?";b:0;s:7:"public?";b:1;s:7:"hidden?";b:0;s:8:"current?";b:0;s:10:"favourite?";b:0;s:6:"images";a:0:{}s:6:"thumbs";a:0:{}s:21:"source-main-image-url";s:0:"";s:9:"og-images";a:0:{}s:16:"og-images-thumbs";a:0:{}s:4:"tags";a:3:{i:0;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:33:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";s:8:"current?";b:0;}i:1;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:45:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";s:8:"current?";b:0;}i:2;a:4:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:5:"scoro";s:4:"href";s:35:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/scoro/";s:8:"current?";b:1;}}s:15:"sharing-buttons";b:0;s:7:"related";b:0;s:9:"read-href";s:74:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/all/scoro-relocates-eli-chat-to-help-station/read/";s:12:"preview-href";b:0;s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:19:"comments-count-text";s:9:"0 comment";s:18:"new-comments-count";b:0;s:23:"new-comments-count-text";s:0:"";s:14:"comments-link?";b:1;s:13:"href-comments";s:78:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/all/scoro-relocates-eli-chat-to-help-station/#comments";}i:3;a:32:{s:2:"id";i:40;s:5:"title";s:44:"Scoro adds export/import workflow for roles";s:4:"href";s:72:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/all/scoro-adds-export-import-workflow-for-roles/";s:13:"href-original";s:72:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/all/scoro-adds-export-import-workflow-for-roles/";s:4:"time";a:2:{i:0;i:1768654800;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1768567293;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:545:"<p>Scoro introduced a bulk-management workflow for roles:</p>
<p>Export the full roles list as CSV or XLS from Settings → Sales and finance → Roles</p>
<p>Edit values (e. g., pricing) in the file</p>
<p>Import the file to apply updates, while leaving unchanged roles intact</p>
<p>The export includes a role initials column (not visible in the UI yet, but available in export).</p>
<p>Learn more: <a href="https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/">https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/</a></p>
